Now to get the densities.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
sequence_counts |> 
  rowwise() |> 
  mutate(
    density = map2(
      water, land, ~tibble(prop = seq(0.0001, 0.9999, length = 100),
                           density_unstd = dbinom(water, size = water + land, prob = prop),
                           density = density_unstd/sum(density_unstd)
                           )
    )
  ) |> 
  unnest(density)->
  density_updates
```
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
density_updates |> 
  ggplot(aes(prop, density))+
    geom_line(aes(group = seq, color = seq))
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![beta distribution updates](index_files/figure-html/fig-beta-updates-1.png){#fig-beta-updates width=576}
:::
